product_description: The Men's Electrostatic Dissipative Work Chukka Driving Moc is a true Twisted X Work original. Handcrafted in full-grain leather and a comfortable air-mesh lining, this Work Chukka Driving Moc showcases an unforgettable comfort, style, and safety in casual footwear. This Twisted X work version of our popular driving moc design blends together a traditional open-laced chukka profile with a moc toe profile. Additionally, the Twisted X CellSole comfort technology integrated into the footbed provides all day cushion and support. The Twisted X driving moc outsole is oil and slip resistant and electrostatic dissipative to prevent a buildup of static eletricity in the body. Twisted X work footwear provides all the comfort, stability, and durability that you need to outperform any demanding work environment.
